{
  "stem": "8569.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Their job was to fill a certain part of whatever it is that was manufactured there with the gunpowder.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were only six girls working in this gunpowder room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was working two department away from her in a little-- in a big room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my job was to measure with a precision instrument a certain part of bakelite, which was called [NON-ENGLISH], for a specific indentation in it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was my job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was very curious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And although we were not allowed to get up from our seat and go to the bathroom-- only with permission, after a while, you got accustomed to the place.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I used to go around the factory, just to look around at what was going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I used to take two little metal boxes that were used for garbage and walk around as if I was, you know, doing something.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And eventually, I used to take these two boxes to my sister.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She used to put a little bit of gunpowder, wrapped up in a little rag tied with a string, into a box and put garbage on the top box.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was walking with these two boxes from my place to her door, and from her door back into my place, and put it under the table and put it inside the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] cuff of my dress because we didn't have pockets.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From there, I used to go to the washroom and in the washroom, share this gunpowder with another girl, with Ella.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] On the way from the factory-- it was about three kilometers to Birkenau where we lived-- we used to carry this on our bodies.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From time to time, there were searches.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
